About Me
Hi! My name is Nabiha Rabbani, and I’m currently a junior at Northside College Prep High School in Chicago, Illinois.
Science Fiction and Techno Orientalism
Do Americans turn to science fiction when threatened with East Asian success?
Goals
*Contribute to existing discussions about techno orientalism
*Create visuals that are easy to understand
+I don’t know how to tally up the variables that I need, and it’s making my graph confusing
